        Udaipur
        If <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Jaisalmer</ENAMEX> is the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">city</ENAMEX> of the desert, then <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Udaipuri</ENAMEX> is
