        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">temple</ENAMEX> was built in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the 13th century</TIMEX>, but the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">sikhara</ENAMEX> toppled, its
        porous stone ruined by storms and <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">plunderers‚ÄÇ‚Äî‚ÄÇand</ENAMEX> by the ambitious
